name: What to spend money on?.
description:
Today this guy has a lot of money ... the question is ... What the fuck to buy? some gold teeth, flowers, socks or a deck ... The reality is that this guy only buys drugs.
Some nice plants and a bueaty church on fire.

Everything is hand made. Acrylic and tattoo pigment on 300g watercolor paper. 

I HOPE YOU ENJOY THIS NFT. 
Thanks a lot for everything!!.
